{
  "stem": "2713.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you shouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, but I didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no, I promised my father that I would be back as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the morning, I got up very early again, and my mother made me breakfast.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the way, right through, I had a terrific ride.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a much better ride than I had the first time, because I knew already, and no one stopped me or anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I arrived-- and when I was close to home, I was the happiest person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I did it for my father, what he wanted me to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came home, [SOBBING] I have never seen my father-- he just took me in his hands, and he was crying.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] And I was really happy that I could do this for him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did 240-- 240 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I left very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left about, say, between 4 and 5 o'clock in the morning, because that's the one thing I wanted to do, because I was afraid, very much, at night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wouldn't go from here to there at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and this is what I did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had no problem at all. 120 kilometers I made a day on the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the restaurant was bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the menswear, when we took a car-- we had a big car-- and we took as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took out, to Dzialoszyce, everything from the menswear store, whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we couldn't take everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we left the things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- when the Germans came in, they took everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
